{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1779332179510,"sessionID":"ses_1b79b3d6dffeHVZBajv0rOolrR","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"task","callID":"call_01_YQABcEztqLW60QB5bMAi6157","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"description":"QA story: 02-login renter login","subagent_type":"general","prompt":"You are a Playwright QA agent. Execute this story and return results.\n\nSTORY: Renter login with email and password (02-login)\nROLE: all (unauthenticated guest who logs in as renter)\nFRONTEND_URL: http://localhost:5173\nRUN_DIR: /Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/status/story-runs/2026-05-21T02:37:19Z/02-login\nSTORY_YAML: /Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/user_stories/02-login.yaml\nFIXTURES: /Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/user_stories/_fixtures.yaml\n\nCREDENTIALS (from _fixtures.yaml users.renter):\n  email: jane@example.com\n  password: Password123!\n\nIMPORTANT: You MUST use @playwright/cli via bash commands (npx playwright). Do NOT write .spec.ts files.\n\nEXECUTION PLAN:\nExecute each step using playwright-cli bash commands. Take screenshot after each step (save to RUN_DIR/step-NN.png).\n\nWORKFLOW:\n\nStep 1 (AC-1): Submit valid email and password credentials to log in as a renter\n  - Do: npx playwright open http://localhost:5173/login --viewport-size=1280,800\n  - Do: npx playwright fill --selector \"input[type=email]\" --value \"jane@example.com\"\n  - Do: npx playwright fill --selector \"input[type=password]\" --value \"Password123!\"\n  - Do: npx playwright screenshot RUN_DIR/step-01a.png\n  - Do: npx playwright click --selector \"button[type=submit]\"\n  - Do: Wait for navigation/redirect to complete\n  - Assert: request POST matching \"(login|signin|auth)\" status 2xx\n  - Assert: URL path is \"/home\" or page shows property search/home content\n  - Do: npx playwright screenshot RUN_DIR/step-01b.png\n\nStep 2 (AC-2): Click \"Forgot password?\" link to navigate to the forgot password page\n  - Do: npx playwright open http://localhost:5173/login --viewport-size=1280,800\n  - Do: npx playwright click --selector \"a:has-text('Forgot')\" or \"text=Forgot\"\n  - Assert: URL path contains \"/forgot-password\"\n  - Do: npx playwright screenshot RUN_DIR/step-02.png\n\nStep 3 (AC-3): Click \"Create one\" link to navigate to the signup page\n  - Do: npx playwright open http://localhost:5173/login --viewport-size=1280,800\n  - Do: npx playwright click --selector \"a:has-text('Create')\" or \"text=Create one\" or \"text=Sign up\"\n  - Assert: URL path contains \"/signup\"\n  - Do: npx playwright screenshot RUN_DIR/step-03.png\n\nStep 4 (BC-1): Email field empty - form validation prevents submission\n  - Do: npx playwright open http://localhost:5173/login --viewport-size=1280,800\n  - Do: npx playwright click --selector \"button[type=submit]\"\n  - Assert: text \"required\" visible OR the email field shows validation error\n  - Do: npx playwright screenshot RUN_DIR/step-04.png\n\nStep 5 (BC-2): Password field empty - form validation prevents submission\n  - Do: npx playwright open http://localhost:5173/login --viewport-size=1280,800\n  - Do: npx playwright fill --selector \"input[type=email]\" --value \"jane@example.com\"\n  - Do: npx playwright click --selector \"button[type=submit]\"\n  - Assert: text \"required\" visible OR password field shows validation error\n  - Do: npx playwright screenshot RUN_DIR/step-05.png\n\nStep 6 (BC-3): Email exceeds max length - server returns 400 validation error\n  - Do: npx playwright open http://localhost:5173/login --viewport-size=1280,800\n  - Do: npx playwright fill --selector \"input[type=email]\" --value \"aaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaa@test.com\" (255+