lt | Screenshot |\n|------|--------|--------|------------|\n| 1 | AC-1: Login with valid renter credentials | PASS/FAIL | step-01b.png |\n| 2 | AC-2: Navigate to forgot password | PASS/FAIL | step-02.png |\n| 3 | AC-3: Navigate to signup | PASS/FAIL | step-03.png |\n| 4 | BC-1: Empty email validation | PASS/FAIL | step-04.png |\n| 5 | BC-2: Empty password validation | PASS/FAIL | step-05.png |\n| 6 | BC-3: Email max length 400 error | PASS/FAIL | step-06.png |\n| 7 | ES-1: Invalid credentials 401 | PASS/FAIL | step-07.png |\n| 8 | ES-2: Suspended account 403 | PASS/FAIL | step-08.png |\n| 9 | ES-3: No console errors on load | PASS/FAIL | step-09.png |\n| 10 | Final: no failed requests | PASS/FAIL | step-10.png |\nFAILURE_DETAILS: (if any failures, explain. If PASS, write \"none\")\nSUGGESTED_STORIES: (0-3 new story names if gaps found)"},"output":"task_id: ses_1b797c650ffedcMDYV3T74g527 (for resuming to continue this task if needed)\n\n<task_result>\nAll steps executed. Here are the results:\n\n---\n\nSTATUS: FAIL\nSTORY: 02-login\n| Step | Action | Result | Screenshot |\n|------|--------|--------|------------|\n| 1 | AC-1: Login with valid renter credentials | PASS | step-01b.png |\n| 2 | AC-2: Navigate to forgot password | PASS | step-02.png |\n| 3 | AC-3: Navigate to signup | PASS | step-03.png |\n| 4 | BC-1: Empty email validation | PASS | step-04.png |\n| 5 | BC-2: Empty password validation | PASS | step-05.png |\n| 6 | BC-3: Email max length 400 error | FAIL | step-06.png |\n| 7 | ES-1: Invalid credentials 401 | FAIL | step-07.png |\n| 8 | ES-2: Suspended account 403 | FAIL | step-08.png |\n| 9 | ES-3: No console errors on load | PASS | step-09.png |\n| 10 | Final: no failed requests | PASS | step-10.png |\nFAILURE_DETAILS: Static HTML prototype lacks server-side validation. Steps 6-8 all navigate to /05-home.html regardless of input: (BC-3) 255+ char email submits without maxlength/rejection; (ES-1) wrong password logs in normally; (ES-2) suspended account lo