ack')\" or \"text=Back to login\" or \"text=Sign in\" or \"text=Login\"\n  - Assert: URL path contains \"/login\"\n  - Do: npx playwright screenshot RUN_DIR/step-02.png\n\nStep 3 (BC-1): Email field empty - form validation prevents submission\n  - Do: npx playwright open http://localhost:5173/forgot-password --viewport-size=1280,800\n  - Do: npx playwright click --selector \"button[type=submit]\"\n  - Assert: text \"required\" visible OR email field shows validation\n  - Do: npx playwright screenshot RUN_DIR/step-03.png\n\nStep 4 (BC-2): Enter email not registered - server still returns 200 with generic message\n  - Do: npx playwright open http://localhost:5173/forgot-password --viewport-size=1280,800\n  - Do: npx playwright fill --selector \"input[type=email]\" --value \"nonexistent@example.com\"\n  - Do: npx playwright click --selector \"button[type=submit]\"\n  - Assert: request POST matching \"forgot\" status 2xx (generic message, no user enumeration)\n  - Do: npx playwright screenshot RUN_DIR/step-04.png\n\nStep 5 (BC-3): Malformed email - 400 validation error\n  - Do: npx playwright open http://localhost:5173/forgot-password --viewport-size=1280,800\n  - Do: npx playwright fill --selector \"input[type=email]\" --value \"notanemail\"\n  - Do: npx playwright click --selector \"button[type=submit]\"\n  - Assert: request POST matching \"forgot\" status 4xx OR text \"valid\" or \"email\" error visible\n  - Do: npx playwright screenshot RUN_DIR/step-05.png\n\nStep 6 (ES-1): Invalid email format (e.g. 'notanemail') - field-level error shown\n  - Do: npx playwright open http://localhost:5173/forgot-password --viewport-size=1280,800\n  - Do: npx playwright fill --selector \"input[type=email]\" --value \"notanemail\"\n  - Do: npx playwright click --selector \"button[type=submit]\"\n  - Assert: text \"valid\" or \"email\" error visible on page\n  - Do: npx playwright screenshot RUN_DIR/step-06.png\n\nStep 7 (ES-2): Page loads without console errors\n  - Do: npx playwright open http://localhost:5173/forgot-password --viewport-size=1280,800\n  - Assert: no console errors on page load\n  - Do: npx playwright screenshot RUN_DIR/step-07.png\n\nRETURN FORMAT — you MUST return exactly this structure at the end:\n\nSTATUS: PASS|FAIL|CRASH\nSTORY: 04-forgot-password\n| Step | Action | Result | Screenshot |\n|------|--------|--------|------------|\n| 1 | AC-1: Submit registered email for reset | PASS/FAIL | step-01b.png |\n| 2 | AC-2: Navigate back to login | PASS/FAIL | step-02.png |\n| 3 | BC-1: Empty email validation | PASS/FAIL | step-03.png |\n| 4 | BC-2: Unregistered email returns 200 | PASS/FAIL | step-04.png |\n| 5 | BC-3: Malformed email 400 | PASS/FAIL | step-05.png |\n| 6 | ES-1: Invalid email format error shown | PASS/FAIL | step-06.png |\n| 7 | ES-2: No console errors | PASS/FAIL | step-07.png |\nFAILURE_DETAILS: (if any failures, explain. If PASS, write \"none\")\nSUGGESTED_STORIES: (0-3 new story names if gaps found)"},"output":"task_id: ses_1b796005effexJkhDVZbvoMAA9 (for resuming to continue this task if needed)\n\n<task_result>\nAll screenshots captured. Here are the results:\n\n---\n\n**STATUS: FAIL**\n**STORY: 04-forgot-password**\n\n| Step | Action | Result | Screenshot |\n|------|--------|--------|------------|\n| 1 | AC-1: Submit registered email for reset | FAIL | step-01b.png |\n| 2 | AC-2: Navigate back to login | PASS | step-02.png |\n| 3 | BC-1: Empty email validation | PASS | step-03.png |\n| 4 | BC-2: Unregistered email returns 200 | FAIL | step-04.png |\n| 5 | BC-3: Malformed email 400 | PASS | step-05.png |\n| 6 | ES-1: Invalid email format error shown | PASS | step-06.png |\n| 7 | ES-2: No console errors | FAIL | step-07.png |\n\n**FAILURE_DETAILS:**\n- **Step 1 (AC-1):** Form has `onsubmit=\"event.preventDefault();\"` - no POST request is made to any \"forgot\" endpoint. No confirmation message (\"sent\", \"reset\", or \"email\") appears. The static HTML prototype lacks API integration for form submission.\n- **Step 4 (BC-2):** Same root cause as Step 1 - form submission is prevented by inline JS. No API call fires, so the unregistered-email-200 behavior cannot be verified.\n- **Step 7 (ES-2):** Console has 1 error (favicon.ico 404 - `http://localhost:5173/favicon.ico` returns 404) and 1 warning (Tailwind CDN production warning).\n\n**SUGGESTED_STORIES:**\n- Wire forgot-password form to POST /api/auth/forgot-password with success/error feedback\n- Add favicon.ico to prevent browser console errors\n- Add loading spinner state during form submission (state transition: loading)\n</task_result>","metadata":{"parentSessionId":"ses_1b79b3d6dffeHVZBajv0rOolrR","sessionId":"ses_1b796005effexJkhDVZbvoMAA9","model":{"modelID":"deepseek-v4-pro","providerID":"opencode-go"},"truncated":false},"title":"QA story: 04-forgot-password","time":{"start":1779331366819,"end":1779332634665}},"id":"prt_e48695115001vJ3uKadRE8ZGQT","sessionID":"ses_1b79b3d6dffeHVZBajv0rOolrR","messageID":"msg_e4866aab7001tdtNtwNgmx5NDe"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1779332645219,"sessionID":"ses_1b79b3d6dffeHVZBajv0rOolrR","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"task","callID":"call_00_vnRK2yE5NAezh47bfAac4577","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"description":"QA story: index splash screen","subagent_type":"general","prompt":"You are a Playwright QA agent. Execute this story and return results.\n\nSTORY: Splash screen with automatic redirect to property search (index)\nROLE: all (unauthenticated guest)\nFRONTEND_URL: http://localhost:5173\nRUN_DIR: /Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/status/story-runs/2026-05-21T02:37:19Z/index\nSTORY_YAML: /Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/user_stories/index.yaml\nFIXTURES: /Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/user_stories/_fixtures.yaml\n\nIMPORTANT: You MUST use @playwright/cli via bash commands (npx playwright). Do NOT write .spec.ts files. Use the `open`, `fill`, `click`, `textContent`, `screenshot`, `waitFor` etc. commands directly.\n\nEXECUTION PLAN:\nExecute each workflow step below using playwright-cli bash commands. Take a screenshot after each step (save to RUN_DIR/step-NN.png). For each step, report:\n\nStep N: [Action Description]\n  Action: [what you did]\n  Result: PASS | FAIL | SKIP\n  Screenshot: step-NN.png\n  Note: [brief observation]\n\nWORKFLOW:\n\nStep 1 (AC-1): Navigate to / then Assert text \"NestFind\" visible and Assert text \"Finding your way home\" visible\n  - Do: npx playwright open http://localhost:5173/ --viewport-size=1280,800\n  - Do: npx playwright screenshot RUN_DIR/step-01.png\n  - Assert: text \"NestFind\" is visible on the page\n  - Assert: text \"Finding your way home\" is visible on the page\n\nStep 2 (AC-2): After ~2 seconds, browser auto-redirects to property search home page\n  - Do: npx playwright waitFor --text \"Search\" OR waitFor --url \"**/home\" --timeout 10000\n  - Do: npx playwright screenshot RUN_DIR/step-02.png\n  - Assert: URL path matches \"/home\" or \"/05-home\" or page contains property search content\n\nStep 3 (BC-1): Slow network - splash screen remains visible beyond 2 seconds; loading indicator animates\n  - Do: npx playwright open http://localhost:5173/ --viewport-size=1280,800\n  - Verify: a loading indicator/bar/spinner is visible on the splash screen\n\nStep 4 (BC-2): Basic page loads without JavaScript errors (graceful fallback check)\n  - Do: npx playwright open http://localhost:5173/ --viewport-size=1280,800\n  - Assert: no console errors on page load\n\nStep 5 (ES-1): Verify home/target page doesn't return 404 after redirect\n  - Do: npx playwright open http://localhost:5173/ --viewport-size=1280,800\n  - Do: Wait for redirect to complete (up to 10s)\n  - Assert: no 404 text on final page\n  - Assert: no console errors\n\nStep 6 (ES-2): Splash page loads and doesn't crash on network issues (verify it at least renders)\n  - Do: npx playwright open http://localhost:5173/ --viewport-size=1280,800\n  - Assert: page body is not empty (content loads)\n\nRETURN FORMAT — you MUST return exactly this structure at the end:\n\nSTATUS: PASS|FAIL|CRASH\nSTORY: index\n| Step | Action | Result | Screenshot |\n|------|--------|--------|------------|\n| 1 | AC-1: Assert text NestFind and tagline visible | PASS/FAIL | step-01.png |\n| 2 | AC-2: Auto-redirect to property search | PASS/FAIL | step-02.png |\n| 3 | BC-1: Loading indicator on splash | PASS/FAIL | step-03.png |\n| 4 | BC-2: No console errors on load | PASS/FAIL | step-04.png |\n| 5 | ES-1: Target page not 404 after redirect | PASS/FAIL | step-05.png |\n| 6 | ES-2: Page renders without crash | PASS/FAIL | step-06.png |\nFAILURE_DETAILS: (if any failures, explain what happened. If PASS, write \"none\")\nSUGGESTED_STORIES: (if you notice missing test coverage, suggest 0-3 new story names)"},"output":"task_id: ses_1b798af9effeD4lVWj6zHZIuy4 (for resuming to continue this task if needed)\n\n<task_result>\nHere is the final test report:\n\n---\n\n**STATUS: FAIL**\n**STORY: index**\n\n| Step | Action | Result | Screenshot |\n|------|--------|--------|------------|\n| 1 | AC-1: Assert text NestFind and tagline visible | PASS | step-01.png |\n| 2 | AC-2: Auto-redirect to property search | PASS | step-02.png |\n| 3 | BC-1: Loading indicator on splash | PASS | step-03.png |\n| 4 | BC-2: No console errors on load | FAIL | step-04.png |\n| 5 | ES-1: Target page not 404 after redirect | PASS | step-05.png |\n| 6 | ES-2: Page renders without crash | PASS | step-06.png |\n\n**FAILURE_DETAILS:** Step 4 — Console error on splash page load: `[ERROR] Failed to load resource: the server responded with a status of 404 (File not found) @ http://localhost:5173/favicon.ico:0`. This is a missing favicon.ico (network resource 404), not a JavaScript runtime error. The page functions correctly despite this. Also present: Tailwind CDN warning (non-blocking). No JS runtime errors were detected.\n\n**SUGGESTED_STORIES:**\n- `index-js-disabled` — Verify splash screen stays static when JavaScript is disabled (no redirect occurs; this matches the true BC-2 boundary case in the story YAML)\n- `index-missing-assets` — Verify splash screen renders gracefully when supporting assets (favicon, fonts, CDN scripts) fail to load\n</task_result>","metadata":{"parentSessionId":"ses_1b79b3d6dffeHVZBajv0rOolrR","sessionId":"ses_1b798af9effeD4lVWj6zHZIuy4","model":{"modelID":"deepseek-v4-pro","providerID":"opencode-go"},"truncated":false},"title":"QA story: index splash screen","time":{"start":1779331190885,"end":1779332645218}},"id":"prt_e4866c0db001cDfHK3pNoFYDoz","sessionID":"ses_1b79b3d6dffeHVZBajv0rOolrR","messageID":"msg_e4866aab7001tdtNtwNgmx5NDe"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1779333013377,"sessionID":"ses_1b79b3d6dffeHVZBajv0rOolrR","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"task","callID":"call_02_UZDSdisgsp4vfhdh74Io4598","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"description":"QA story: 03-signup registration","subagent_type":"general","prompt":"You are a Playwright QA agent. Execute this story and return results.\n\nSTORY: Self-service renter registration (03-signup)\nROLE: all (unauthenticated guest registering as renter)\nFRONTEND_URL: http://localhost:5173\nRUN_DIR: /Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/status/story-runs/2026-05-21T02:37:19Z/03-signup\nSTORY_YAML: /Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/user_stories/03-signup.yaml\nFIXTURES: /Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/user_stories/_fixtures.yaml\n\nCREDENTIALS (from _fixtures.yaml users.renter):\n  name: Jane Doe\n  email: jane@example.com\n  password: Password123!\n  phone: (555) 123-4567\n\nIMPORTANT: You MUST use @playwright/cli via bash commands (npx playwright). Do NOT write .spec.ts files. Take screenshot after each step (save to RUN_DIR/step-NN.png).\n\nWORKFLOW:\n\nStep 1 (AC-1): Fill all required fields (name, email, password min 8 chars) and submit\n  - Do: npx playwright open http://localhost:5173/signup --viewport-size=1280,800\n  - Do: npx playwright fill --selector \"input[name=name]\" --value \"Test User\"\n  - Do: npx playwright fill --selector \"input[type=email]\" --value \"test-register@example.com\"\n  - Do: npx playwright fill --selector \"input[type=password]\" --value \"Password123!\"\n  - Do: npx playwright screenshot RUN_DIR/step-01a.png\n  - Do: npx playwright click --selector \"button[type=submit]\"\n  - Do: Wait for navigation/redirect\n  - Assert: request POST matching \"register\" status 2xx\n  - Assert: URL path is \"/home\" or page shows home content\n  - Do: npx playwright screenshot RUN_DIR/step-01b.png\n\nStep 2 (AC-2): Fill all fields including optional phone number and submit\n  - Do: npx playwright open http://localhost:5173/signup --viewport-size=1280,800\n  - Do: npx playwright fill --selector \"input[name=name]\" --value \"Phone User\"\n  - Do: npx playwright fill --selector \"input[type=email]\" --value \"test-phone@example.com\"\n  - Do: npx playwright fill --selector \"input[type=password]\" --value \"Password123!\"\n  - Do: npx playwright fill --selector \"input[type=tel]\" --value \"(555) 123-4567\"\n  - Do: npx playwright screenshot RUN_DIR/step-02a.png\n  - Do: npx playwright click --selector \"button[type=submit]\"\n  - Assert: request POST matching \"register\" status 2xx\n  - Do: npx playwright screenshot RUN_DIR/step-02b.png\n\nStep 3 (AC-3): Click \"Log in\" link to navigate to the login page\n  - Do: npx playwright open http://localhost:5173/signup --viewport-size=1280,800\n  - Do: npx playwright click --selector \"a:has-text('Log in')\" or \"text=Log in\" or \"text=Sign in\"\n  - Assert: URL path contains \"/login\"\n  - Do: npx playwright screenshot RUN_DIR/step-03.png\n\nStep 4 (BC-1): Password fewer than 8 characters - validation prevents submission\n  - Do: npx playwright open http://localhost:5173/signup --viewport-size=1280,800\n  - Do: npx playwright fill --selector \"input[name=name]\" --value \"Test\"\n  - Do: npx playwright fill --selector \"input[type=email]\" --value \"test@example.com\"\n  - Do: npx playwright fill --selector \"input[type=password]\" --value \"Short1\"\n  - Do: npx playwright click --selector \"button[type=submit]\"\n  - Assert: text \"minimum\" or \"8\" visible OR password validation error shown\n  - Do: npx playwright screenshot RUN_DIR/step-04.png\n\nStep 5 (BC-2): Name field empty - form validation prevents submission\n  - Do: npx playwright open http://localhost:5173/signup --viewport-size=1280,800\n  - Do: npx playwright fill --selector \"input[type=email]\" --value \"test@example.com\"\n  - Do: npx playwright fill --selector \"input[type=password]\" --value \"Password123!\"\n  - Do: npx playwright click --selector \"button[type=submit]\"\n  - Assert: text \"required\" visible OR name field validation error shown\n  - Do: npx playwright screenshot RUN_DIR/step-05.png\n\nStep 6 (BC-3): Phone field left empty - submission succeeds\n  - Do: npx playwright open http://localhost:5173/signup --viewport-size=1280,800\n  - Do: npx playwright fill --selector \"input[name=name]\" --value \"NoPhone User\"\n  - Do: npx playwright fill --selector \"input[type=email]\" --value \"test-nophone@example.com\"\n  - Do: npx playwright fill --selector \"input[type=password]\" --value \"Password123!\"\n  - Do: npx playwright click --selector \"button[type=submit]\"\n  - Assert: request POST matching \"register\" status 2xx (phone being optional should not block)\n  - Do: npx playwright screenshot RUN_DIR/step-06.png\n\nStep 7 (BC-4): Name at max 100 characters accepted\n  - Do: npx playwright open http://localhost:5173/signup --viewport-size=1280,800\n  - Do: npx playwright fill --selector \"input[name=name]\" --value \"AAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAA\" (100 A's)\n  - Do: npx playwright fill --selector \"input[type=email]\" --value \"test-longname@example.com\"\n  - Do: npx playwright fill --selector \"input[type=password]\" --value \"Password123!\"\n  - Do: npx playwright click --selector \"button[type=submit]\"\n  - Assert: request POST matching \"register\" status 2xx\n  - Do: npx playwright screenshot RUN_DIR/step-07.png\n\nStep 8 (ES-1): Email already registered - server returns 409 Conflict\n  - Do: npx playwright open http://localhost:5173/signup --viewport-size=1280,800\n  - Do: npx playwright fill --selector \"input[name=name]\" --value \"Jane Doe\"\n  - Do: npx playwright fill --selector \"input[type=email]\" --value \"jane@example.com\"\n  - Do: npx playwright fill --selector \"input[type=password]\" --value \"Password123!\"\n  - Do: npx playwright click --selector \"button[type=submit]\"\n  - Assert: request POST matching \"register\" status 409 OR text \"already\" visible\n  - Do: npx playwright screenshot RUN_DIR/step-08.png\n\nStep 9 (ES-2): Invalid email format - server returns 400\n  - Do: npx playwright open http://localhost:5173/signup --viewport-size=1280,800\n  - Do: npx playwright fill --selector \"input[name=name]\" --value \"Test\"\n  - Do: npx playwright fill --selector \"input[type=email]\" --value \"notanemail\"\n  - Do: npx playwright fill --selector \"input[type=password]\" --value \"Password123!\"\n  - Do: npx playwright click --selector \"button[type=submit]\"\n  - Assert: request POST matching \"register\" status 4xx OR text \"invalid\" or \"valid email\" visible\n  - Do: npx playwright screenshot RUN_DIR/step-09.png\n\nStep 10 (ES-3): Page loads without errors\n  - Do: npx playwright open http://localhost:5173/signup --viewport-size=1280,800\n  - Assert: no console errors on page load\n  - Do: npx playwright screenshot RUN_DIR/step-10.png\n\nRETURN FORMAT — you MUST return exactly this structure at the end:\n\nSTATUS: PASS|FAIL|CRASH\nSTORY: 03-signup\n| Step | Action | Result | Screenshot |\n|------|--------|--------|------------|\n| 1 | AC-1: Register with required fields | PASS/FAIL | step-01b.png |\n| 2 | AC-2: Register with phone included | PASS/FAIL | step-02b.png |\n| 3 | AC-3: Navigate to login page | PASS/FAIL | step-03.png |\n| 4 | BC-1: Password too short validation | PASS/FAIL | step-04.png |\n| 5 | BC-2: Empty name validation | PASS/FAIL | step-05.png |\n| 6 | BC-3: Optional phone empty succeeds | PASS/FAIL | step-06.png |\n| 7 | BC-4: Max length name accepted | PASS/FAIL | step-07.png |\n| 8 | ES-1: Duplicate email 409 | PASS/FAIL | step-08.png |\n| 9 | ES-2: Invalid email format 400 | PASS/FAIL | step-09.png |\n| 10 | ES-3: No console errors | PASS/FAIL | step-10.png |\nFAILURE_DETAILS: (if any failures, explain. If PASS, write \"none\")\nSUGGESTED_STORIES: (0-3 new story names if gaps found)"},"output":"task_id: ses_1b796b01fffelIAClaW8grmIoj (for resuming to continue this task if needed)\n\n<task_result>\nAll 10 steps executed and 12 screenshots saved. Here are the results:\n\n---\n\nSTATUS: FAIL\nSTORY: 03-signup\n| Step | Action | Result | Screenshot |\n|------|--------|--------|------------|\n| 1 | AC-1: Register with required fields | PASS | step-01b.png |\n| 2 | AC-2: Register with phone included | PASS | step-02b.png |\n| 3 | AC-3: Navigate to login page | PASS | step-03.png |\n| 4 | BC-1: Password too short validation | PASS | step-04.png |\n| 5 | BC-2: Empty name validation | PASS | step-05.png |\n| 6 | BC-3: Optional phone empty succeeds | PASS | step-06.png |\n| 7 | BC-4: Max length name accepted | PASS | step-07.png |\n| 8 | ES-1: Duplicate email 409 | FAIL | step-08.png |\n| 9 | ES-2: Invalid email format 400 | PASS | step-09.png |\n| 10 | ES-3: No console errors | PASS | step-10.png |\nFAILURE_DETAILS: Step 8 (ES-1): Form submitted with already-registered email \"jane@example.com\" but redirected to home (/05-home.html) instead of showing a 409 Conflict or \"already\" error. The static HTML prototype has no backend server, so duplicate email detection is not implemented. Step 1 and Step 2 also lack POST requests to a \"register\" endpoint — these are expected limitations of the static HTML prototype but mean full AC cannot be verified without the backend.\nSUGGESTED_STORIES:\n- 04-backend-signup-api: Implement POST /api/auth/register endpoint with server-side validation (duplicate email 409, invalid format 400, name length constraints)\n- 05-signup-api-integration: Connect signup form to backend API with proper error display for 409/400/422 responses\n</task_result>","metadata":{"parentSessionId":"ses_1b79b3d6dffeHVZBajv0rOolrR","sessionId":"ses_1b796b01fffelIAClaW8grmIoj","model":{"modelID":"deepseek-v4-pro","providerID":"opencode-go"},"truncated":false},"title":"QA story: 03-signup registration","time":{"start":1779331321827,"end":1779333013375}},"id":"prt_e48683b1f001aYaPOMzvxDqXNd","sessionID":"ses_1b79b3d6dffeHVZBajv0rOolrR","messageID":"msg_e4866aab7001tdtNtwNgmx5NDe"}}
