{"type":"step_start","timestamp":1779333015924,"sessionID":"ses_1b79b3d6dffeHVZBajv0rOolrR","part":{"id":"prt_e48832971001qzKJKeEBSU87o9","messageID":"msg_e488320100010ShcrNtE5mrsmW","sessionID":"ses_1b79b3d6dffeHVZBajv0rOolrR","snapshot":"285a6157892b78da45b88cd7ac23a9d5c544208e","type":"step-start"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1779333025652,"sessionID":"ses_1b79b3d6dffeHVZBajv0rOolrR","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_00_qFJvt37VJeQ8I0i1LEJk9806","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/user_stories/05-home.yaml"},"output":"<path>/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/user_stories/05-home.yaml</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: id: US-05-HOME\n2: role: renter\n3: feature: Search and browse rental property listings\n4: page: 05-home.html\n5: goal: |\n6:   A renter searches for rental properties by location, filters by price,\n7:   bedrooms, and property type, and browses paginated property cards.\n8: \n9: acceptance_criteria:\n10:   - id: AC-1\n11:     description: View property listings grid showing cards with thumbnail, price, beds, baths, sqft, and property type badge\n12:     ui_route: /home\n13:     endpoint: GET /api/properties\n14:     expected: \"200 OK, grid displays property cards with correct data, count header shows 'N properties found'\"\n15:   - id: AC-2\n16:     description: Enter a location in the search input and click Search to filter results\n17:     ui_route: /home\n18:     endpoint: GET /api/properties?search=San+Francisco\n19:     expected: \"200 OK, results filtered to properties matching the search term\"\n20:   - id: AC-3\n21:     description: Select a price range filter to narrow results by budget\n22:     ui_route: /home\n23:     endpoint: GET /api/properties?minPrice=2000&maxPrice=3000\n24:     expected: \"200 OK, only properties within the selected price range are shown\"\n25:   - id: AC-4\n26:     description: Click \"Load more properties\" to fetch the next page of results\n27:     ui_route: /home\n28:     endpoint: GET /api/properties?page=2\n29:     expected: \"200 OK, new property cards appends to the grid, total count updates\"\n30:   - id: AC-5\n31:     description: Toggle the heart icon on a property card to save/unsave to favorites\n32:     ui_route: /home\n33:     endpoint: POST /api/favorites or DELETE /api/favorites/:propertyId\n34:     expected: \"Heart icon fills/unfills, 201/200 response appropriately\"\n35: \n36: boundary_cases:\n37:   - case: \"Search returns zero results — grid shows empty state with 'No properties found' message and suggestion to broaden filters\"\n38:   - case: \"All filters at extremes (max price $0, no bedrooms filter, all types) — returns all non-archived properties\"\n39:   - case: \"Load more on last page — button disappears or shows 'You've seen all N properties'\"\n40: \n41: error_scenarios:\n42:   - scenario: \"Unauthenticated user tries to toggle favorite — server returns 401, redirect to login or heart icon silently fails\"\n43:   - scenario: \"API returns 500 — grid shows error state with retry button\"\n44:   - scenario: \"Network failure during search — loading skeleton disappears, inline error toast shown\"\n45: \n46: state_transitions:\n47:   - state: loading\n48:     expected: \"Skeleton cards (gray placeholder rectangles) shown in grid while data fetches\"\n49:   - state: empty\n50:     expected: \"Empty state with illustration and 'No properties found. Try adjusting your filters.' message\"\n51:   - state: error\n52:     expected: \"Error message with 'Something went wrong' text and a retry button\"\n53: \n54: fixture_refs:\n55:   - users.renter\n56:   - properties.apt_downtown\n57:   - properties.house_palo_alto\n\n(End of file - total 57 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"id: US-05-HOME\nrole: renter\nfeature: Search and browse rental property listings\npage: 05-home.html\ngoal: |\n  A renter searches for rental properties by location, filters by price,\n  bedrooms, and property type, and browses paginated property cards.\n\nacceptance_criteria:\n  - id: AC-1\n    description: View property listings grid showing cards with thumbnail, price, beds, baths, sqft, and property type badge\n    ui_route: /home\n    endpoint: GET /api/properties\n    expected: \"200 OK, grid displays property cards with correct data, count header shows 'N properties found'\"\n  - id: AC-2\n    description: Enter a location in the search input and click Search to filter results\n    ui_route: /home\n    endpoint: GET /api/properties?search=San+Francisco\n    expected: \"200 OK, results filtered to properties matching the search term\"\n  - id: AC-3","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":".claude-project/nestfind/user_stories/05-home.yaml","time":{"start":1779333025349,"end":1779333025649}},"id":"prt_e48834945001pH3KpqIufU4aT4","sessionID":"ses_1b79b3d6dffeHVZBajv0rOolrR","messageID":"msg_e488320100010ShcrNtE5mrsmW"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1779333027363,"sessionID":"ses_1b79b3d6dffeHVZBajv0rOolrR","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_01_M6MeAMZNuqN7eExV8KMc6837","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/user_stories/06-property-detail.yaml"},"output":"<path>/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/user_stories/06-property-detail.yaml</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: id: US-06-PROPERTY-DETAIL\n2: role: renter\n3: feature: View full property details, photos, amenities, and location\n4: page: 06-property-detail.html\n5: goal: |\n6:   A renter views a property's full details including photo gallery, description,\n7:   amenities, location map, and pricing. They can save the property to favorites\n8:   and proceed to submit an inquiry.\n9: \n10: acceptance_criteria:\n11:   - id: AC-1\n12:     description: Navigate to property detail page and view photo gallery, specs, description, amenities, and location map\n13:     ui_route: /properties/:id\n14:     endpoint: GET /api/properties/:id\n15:     expected: \"200 OK, all sections rendered: photo gallery, title, address, beds/baths/sqft, about text, amenities grid, map placeholder\"\n16:   - id: AC-2\n17:     description: Click \"Contact About Property\" button to open the inquiry modal\n18:     ui_route: /properties/:id\n19:     endpoint: none (opens modal, see 07-inquiry-modal)\n20:     expected: \"Inquiry modal opens with property mini-card pre-populated\"\n21:   - id: AC-3\n22:     description: Toggle \"Save to Favorites\" button to add/remove from favorites\n23:     ui_route: /properties/:id\n24:     endpoint: POST /api/favorites or DELETE /api/favorites/:propertyId\n25:     expected: \"Heart fills red when favorited, returns to outline when unfavorited, 201/200 response\"\n26: \n27: boundary_cases:\n28:   - case: \"Property has zero photos — photo gallery shows a placeholder image (gray box)\"\n29:   - case: \"Property has zero amenities — amenities section shows 'No amenities listed'\"\n30:   - case: \"Property ID is invalid UUID format — server returns 400 Bad Request\"\n31: \n32: error_scenarios:\n33:   - scenario: \"Property not found (404) — page shows a 'Property not found' message with link back to search\"\n34:   - scenario: \"Archived/soft-deleted property (404) — same as not found; no public access\"\n35:   - scenario: \"Favorite toggle fails with 401 (not logged in) — redirect to login or show login prompt\"\n36:   - scenario: \"Network failure loading property — error state with retry CTA\"\n37: \n38: state_transitions:\n39:   - state: loading\n40:     expected: \"Skeleton placeholders for photo gallery, title, specs, description, amenities, and sidebar card\"\n41:   - state: error\n42:     expected: \"Error banner with 'Failed to load property' text and retry button\"\n43:   - state: not_found\n44:     expected: \"404 page or 'Property not found' card with link back to /home\"\n45: \n46: fixture_refs:\n47:   - users.renter\n48:   - properties.apt_downtown\n\n(End of file - total 48 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"id: US-06-PROPERTY-DETAIL\nrole: renter\nfeature: View full property details, photos, amenities, and location\npage: 06-property-detail.html\ngoal: |\n  A renter views a property's full details including photo gallery, description,\n  amenities, location map, and pricing. They can save the property to favorites\n  and proceed to submit an inquiry.\n\nacceptance_criteria:\n  - id: AC-1\n    description: Navigate to property detail page and view photo gallery, specs, description, amenities, and location map\n    ui_route: /properties/:id\n    endpoint: GET /api/properties/:id\n    expected: \"200 OK, all sections rendered: photo gallery, title, address, beds/baths/sqft, about text, amenities grid, map placeholder\"\n  - id: AC-2\n    description: Click \"Contact About Property\" button to open the inquiry modal\n    ui_route: /properties/:id\n    endpoint: none (opens modal, see 07-inquiry-modal)\n    expected: \"Inquiry modal opens with property mini-card pre-populated\"","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":".claude-project/nestfind/user_stories/06-property-detail.yaml","time":{"start":1779333027051,"end":1779333027361}},"id":"prt_e48834f79001MNtBFDC8LsjA4b","sessionID":"ses_1b79b3d6dffeHVZBajv0rOolrR","messageID":"msg_e488320100010ShcrNtE5mrsmW"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1779333029046,"sessionID":"ses_1b79b3d6dffeHVZBajv0rOolrR","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_02_Uuq4eWZya9G3DJz5tSCP6283","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/user_stories/07-inquiry-modal.yaml"},"output":"<path>/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/user_stories/07-inquiry-modal.yaml</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: id: US-07-INQUIRY-MODAL\n2: role: renter\n3: feature: Submit an inquiry about a property\n4: page: 07-inquiry-modal.html\n5: goal: |\n6:   A renter opens the inquiry modal from the property detail page, fills in\n7:   their contact details and message, and submits an inquiry to the property manager.\n8: \n9: acceptance_criteria:\n10:   - id: AC-1\n11:     description: Open inquiry modal and fill all required fields (name, email, message) then submit\n12:     ui_route: /properties/:id (modal overlay)\n13:     endpoint: POST /api/properties/:id/inquiries\n14:     expected: \"201 Created, modal closes, success toast shown\"\n15:   - id: AC-2\n16:     description: Submit inquiry with phone number (optional field) filled\n17:     ui_route: /properties/:id (modal overlay)\n18:     endpoint: POST /api/properties/:id/inquiries\n19:     expected: \"201 Created, phone included in request body\"\n20:   - id: AC-3\n21:     description: Click Cancel or the X close button to dismiss the modal without submitting\n22:     ui_route: /properties/:id (modal overlay)\n23:     endpoint: none\n24:     expected: \"Modal closes, no API call made, user returns to property detail page\"\n25: \n26: boundary_cases:\n27:   - case: \"Message exactly 10 characters (minimum) — accepted; message at 9 characters — 400 validation error\"\n28:   - case: \"Message exactly 2000 characters (maximum) — accepted; message at 2001 characters — 400 validation error\"\n29:   - case: \"Name field empty — form validation prevents submission\"\n30:   - case: \"Email field empty — form validation prevents submission\"\n31:   - case: \"Phone field empty — submission succeeds\"\n32: \n33: error_scenarios:\n34:   - scenario: \"Unauthenticated (401) — modal should not be accessible; if bypassed, server returns 401\"\n35:   - scenario: \"Property not found (404) during submit — error toast 'This property is no longer available'\"\n36:   - scenario: \"Validation error (400) — field-level errors shown inline below each invalid field\"\n37:   - scenario: \"Network failure — submit button re-enabled, inline error message appears\"\n38: \n39: state_transitions:\n40:   - state: loading\n41:     expected: \"Send Inquiry button shows spinner and is disabled, Cancel button also disabled\"\n42:   - state: success\n43:     expected: \"Modal closes, success toast 'Inquiry submitted successfully' appears on property detail page\"\n44:   - state: error\n45:     expected: \"Inline error message(s) appear within the modal form, modal stays open for correction\"\n46: \n47: fixture_refs:\n48:   - users.renter\n49:   - properties.apt_downtown\n\n(End of file - total 49 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"id: US-07-INQUIRY-MODAL\nrole: renter\nfeature: Submit an inquiry about a property\npage: 07-inquiry-modal.html\ngoal: |\n  A renter opens the inquiry modal from the property detail page, fills in\n  their contact details and message, and submits an inquiry to the property manager.\n\nacceptance_criteria:\n  - id: AC-1\n    description: Open inquiry modal and fill all required fields (name, email, message) then submit\n    ui_route: /properties/:id (modal overlay)\n    endpoint: POST /api/properties/:id/inquiries\n    expected: \"201 Created, modal closes, success toast shown\"\n  - id: AC-2\n    description: Submit inquiry with phone number (optional field) filled\n    ui_route: /properties/:id (modal overlay)\n    endpoint: POST /api/properties/:id/inquiries\n    expected: \"201 Created, phone included in request body\"\n  - id: AC-3","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":".claude-project/nestfind/user_stories/07-inquiry-modal.yaml","time":{"start":1779333028725,"end":1779333029045}},"id":"prt_e48835624001LzCwIDU0s9mM6F","sessionID":"ses_1b79b3d6dffeHVZBajv0rOolrR","messageID":"msg_e488320100010ShcrNtE5mrsmW"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1779333030628,"sessionID":"ses_1b79b3d6dffeHVZBajv0rOolrR","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_03_Xw3N2TKuMRf8ijAHv0w83857","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/user_stories/08-favorites.yaml"},"output":"<path>/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/user_stories/08-favorites.yaml</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: id: US-08-FAVORITES\n2: role: renter\n3: feature: View and manage saved/favorited properties\n4: page: 08-favorites.html\n5: goal: |\n6:   A renter views all their favorited properties in a grid, clicks a property\n7:   card to navigate to its detail page, and unfavorites a property by clicking\n8:   the heart icon.\n9: \n10: acceptance_criteria:\n11:   - id: AC-1\n12:     description: View list of all favorited properties with property cards showing thumbnail, price, address, and specs\n13:     ui_route: /favorites\n14:     endpoint: GET /api/favorites\n15:     expected: \"200 OK, grid displays all saved properties, header shows count 'N saved properties'\"\n16:   - id: AC-2\n17:     description: Click a property card to navigate to the property detail page\n18:     ui_route: /favorites\n19:     endpoint: none (client-side navigation)\n20:     expected: \"Navigate to /properties/:id detail page\"\n21:   - id: AC-3\n22:     description: Click the filled heart icon on a card to remove property from favorites\n23:     ui_route: /favorites\n24:     endpoint: DELETE /api/favorites/:propertyId\n25:     expected: \"200 OK, card removed from grid, count decrements\"\n26: \n27: boundary_cases:\n28:   - case: \"No favorites saved — empty state shown with icon, 'No saved properties' message, and CTA to browse properties\"\n29:   - case: \"User un-favorites the last property — grid transitions to empty state\"\n30: \n31: error_scenarios:\n32:   - scenario: \"Unauthenticated (401) — redirect to login page\"\n33:   - scenario: \"Remove favorite fails with 404 (already removed or property deleted) — card still removed from UI gracefully\"\n34:   - scenario: \"Network failure loading favorites — error state with retry CTA\"\n35: \n36: state_transitions:\n37:   - state: loading\n38:     expected: \"Skeleton card placeholders shown in grid\"\n39:   - state: empty\n40:     expected: \"Empty state with heart icon, 'No saved properties yet', and 'Browse Properties' CTA button\"\n41:   - state: error\n42:     expected: \"Error banner with retry button\"\n43: \n44: fixture_refs:\n45:   - users.renter\n\n(End of file - total 45 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"id: US-08-FAVORITES\nrole: renter\nfeature: View and manage saved/favorited properties\npage: 08-favorites.html\ngoal: |\n  A renter views all their favorited properties in a grid, clicks a property\n  card to navigate to its detail page, and unfavorites a property by clicking\n  the heart icon.\n\nacceptance_criteria:\n  - id: AC-1\n    description: View list of all favorited properties with property cards showing thumbnail, price, address, and specs\n    ui_route: /favorites\n    endpoint: GET /api/favorites\n    expected: \"200 OK, grid displays all saved properties, header shows count 'N saved properties'\"\n  - id: AC-2\n    description: Click a property card to navigate to the property detail page\n    ui_route: /favorites\n    endpoint: none (client-side navigation)\n    expected: \"Navigate to /properties/:id detail page\"","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":".claude-project/nestfind/user_stories/08-favorites.yaml","time":{"start":1779333030317,"end":1779333030627}},"id":"prt_e48835c86001517ZjfW61erhuM","sessionID":"ses_1b79b3d6dffeHVZBajv0rOolrR","messageID":"msg_e488320100010ShcrNtE5mrsmW"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1779333056695,"sessionID":"ses_1b79b3d6dffeHVZBajv0rOolrR","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"call_04_dmNFx1K65WA3ABY8aEt97630","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/status/STORY_QA_REPORT_react.md","content":"# Story QA Report\n\ntimestamp: 2026-05-21T02:37:19Z\nrun_dir: /Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/status/story-runs/2026-05-21T02:37:19Z\n\nstories_total: 16\nstories_passed: 0\nstories_failed: 4\nstories_crashed: 0\nstories_skipped: 0\npass_rate: 0.00\n\nbugs_p0: 0\nbugs_p1: 3\nbugs_p2: 1\n\n## Per-Story Results\n\n| story | role | status | priority | first_failure | screenshots |\n|-------|------|--------|----------|---------------|-------------|\n| index | all | FAIL | P2 | BC-2: Console error favicon.ico 404 | story-runs/2026-05-21T02:37:19Z/index/ |\n| 02-login | all | FAIL | P1 | BC-3/ES-1/ES-2: No server-side validation (static HTML) | story-runs/2026-05-21T02:37:19Z/02-login/ |\n| 03-signup | all | FAIL | P1 | ES-1: Duplicate email not rejected (no backend) | story-runs/2026-05-21T02:37:19Z/03-signup/ |\n| 04-forgot-password | all | FAIL | P1 | AC-1: Form submit prevented by JS (no API integration) | story-runs/2026-05-21T02:37:19Z/04-forgot-password/ |\n\n## Failures (one entry per non-PASS story)\n\n### index — P2\n- failure: BC-2: Console error on splash page - favicon.ico 404 (File not found). Also Tailwind CDN warning. No JS runtime errors, page functions correctly.\n- screenshots: story-runs/2026-05-21T02:37:19Z/index/\n- suggested_stories: index-js-disabled (verify graceful fallback when JS disabled), index-missing-assets (render gracefully when favicon/CDN fail)\n\n### 02-login — P1\n- failure: BC-3 (email max length 400), ES-1 (invalid credentials 401), ES-2 (suspended account 403) all FAIL — static HTML prototype lacks server-side validation; form submits and redirects to /05-home.html regardless of input.\n- screenshots: story-runs/2026-05-21T02:37:19Z/02-login/\n- suggested_stories: none\n\n### 03-signup — P1\n- failure: ES-1: Duplicate email \"jane@example.com\" not rejected — redirects to home instead of showing 409 Conflict. Static HTML has no backend API integration.\n- screenshots: story-runs/2026-05-21T02:37:19Z/03-signup/\n- suggested_stories: Backend signup API with server-side validation, Signup form API integration with error display\n\n### 04-forgot-password — P1\n- failure: AC-1: Form has onsubmit=\"event.preventDefault()\" — no POST request fires, no confirmation message appears. BC-2: Same root cause. ES-2: Console error favicon.ico 404.\n- screenshots: story-runs/2026-05-21T02:37:19Z/04-forgot-password/\n- suggested_stories: Wire forgot-password form to POST /api/auth/forgot-password, Add favicon.ico, Add loading spinner state\n\nstory_runner_complete: false\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/status/STORY_QA_REPORT_react.md","exists":true,"truncated":false},"title":".claude-project/nestfind/status/STORY_QA_REPORT_react.md","time":{"start":1779333056384,"end":1779333056692}},"id":"prt_e4883630a001JfANpET3r1bOU5","sessionID":"ses_1b79b3d6dffeHVZBajv0rOolrR","messageID":"msg_e488320100010ShcrNtE5mrsmW"}}
